title: Ivanka Trump, Steve Mnuchin, and Jared Kushner arrive in Israel ahead of embassy move
text:
Ivanka Trump, Steve Mnuchin, and Jared Kushner arrive in Israel ahead of embassy move Sunday, May 13, 2018 - 00:48
U.S. Treasury Secretary, along with Presidnt Trump's daughter Ivanka and son-in-law land at Israel's airport ahead of the US. Embassy in Jerusalem opening. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
